(171, 2, '2019-08-16 06:40:43', '2019-08-16 06:40:43', 'Firecracker is a small cardboard container filled with explosive powder and lit by a fuse.\r\nWhen a small volatile accuse and a fuse in a heavy paper casing, exploded to make noise, called fireworks as at celebrations.\r\nFirecrackers are made by smokeless powder, black powder, and cordite, flash powder with cardboard or plastic.\r\nIt to work best when the entire firecracker must be very tightly packed in order.\r\nFirecrackers are commonly used in the celebration of special festivals, such as Christmas, Independence Day in the United Stat. Country of India used in Diwali. Muslims countries are used in Eid al-Fit and Eid al Azha, Tihar in Nepal, Day of Ashura in Morocco, Guy Fawkes Night or Bonfire Night in the United Kingdom, Halloween in Ireland, Bastille Day in France, Spanish Fallas, in almost every cultural festival of Sri Lanka. New Year\'s Eve and New Year\'s Day, and in the celebration of Chinese New Year by Chinese communities around the world.\r\n\r\nChristmas night is just over a week away and many people will be looking to buy fireworks to ensure their night goes off with a bang.\r\nToday\'s is a modern era so one of the best uses of technology when shopping for fireworks is the ability to use new tools to find the fireworks you love near you. There are several ways available answers to your question when you ask - where can I buy fireworks near me? To find a firework store near you.\r\nMany supermarkets are selling sparklers and fireworks in preparation for November 5, so we\'ve rounded up the best transaction, to ensure your money doesn\'t go up in smoke.\r\n\r\n*** Precaution: Fireworks is a dangerous job.\r\nIt could injure you.\r\nFireworks polluted the environment.\r\nIt creates sound pollution.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Where is fireworks for sale near me ?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'where-is-fireworks-for-sale-near-me', '', '', '2019-08-16 06:40:52', '2019-08-16 06:40:52', '', 0, 'http:/