(186, 2, '2019-08-17 10:44:41', '2019-08-17 10:44:41', 'Christmas Lights:\nChristmas lights are lights used for decoration in celebration of great Christmas festival, normally on display during the Christmas season including arrival and Christmastide. The tradition goes back to while Christmas trees were decorated with candles, which symbolized Christ being the light of the world; these were brought by Christians into their homes.\n \nIn the United States, lights have been produced for especially Christmas and many other holidays. These may be simple sets in usual holiday colors, or the type with plastic ornaments which the light socket fits into. That also produced in typical holiday icons.\n \n \nMagical ways to brighten the holiday’s festival:\nAt Christmas, days are lights used decoration with stylish and practical design. Artificial Christmas led lights are easy to install the light string that does not need to be connected to a mains power supply. Xmas Tree-shaped lights give a distinctive appearance and create a tranquil atmosphere of your garden and your house. Artificial led Christmas lights are ideal for decorating trees, shrubs, parasols, doorways, lawn and indoor items. Also, these led artificial lights are ideal for wedding, Christmas and other festivals’ lighting.\n \nBright & Sparkly Christmas Lighting: On this day there are kinds of led lights for decoration so it’s important to select the perfect artificial led Christmas light for bright and sparkly Christmas lighting. In the circumstance, we suggest to you to consider the following guidelines such as, \n \nTop Lighting Selection:\nAdd warmth and magic to your holiday season with a dazzling array of Christmas lights from The Home Depot. When you are shopping for indoor or outdoor artificial Christmas lights, we have a great selection of twinkle lights, multi-color Christmas tree lights, LED Christmas lights, string lights and more. \n \nIndoor Lighting Options: \nTo bring the Christmas decorations indoors, browse our amazing assortment of artificial Christmas trees. We have a huge selection of pre-lit trees with LED Energy Smart lighting options, including color-changing lights, warm white lights, dual-color options and more. For even more holiday touches, check out our Christmas tree toppers and pre-decorated holiday wreaths and garland – perfect for your mantel or front door. \n\nOutdoor Lighting Options:\nGive your yard a festive flourish with candy cane-shaped Christmas path lights or holiday Luminaria kits. Net lighting is another great outdoor choice: it works well in trees and bushes, comes in a variety of sizes and is easy to set up. To turn your yard into a winter wonderland, add an array of icicle lights across your eaves and awnings or use a Christmas laser light projector, like Star Shower, to project thousands of moving holiday shapes directly onto your home. \n\nMake sure you have enough Options:\nNot sure how many Christmas lights you’ll need? Start with 60 feet of string or icicle lights and add 10-12 feet per awning. Add a light timer for both indoor and outdoor displays to conserve power and ensure your lights consistently shut off at a reasonable hour.\n\n\nSave energy for this Christmas holiday: \nAdd more “green” to your Christmas with our energy-efficient solar-powered Christmas lights. They’re a great alternative to traditional Christmas lights and shine brightly through the night, even in cloudy weather. Both solar-powered and LED battery-powered lights are a convenient and flexible option for Christmas displays. Because they don’t use electricity, there’s no need for extension cords or planning your display around electrical outlets. As an added benefit, you won’t run up your electricity bill. \n\nSourcing Guide for Christmas tree Light:\nOne of the most important of all building systems is the lighting. We offer buyers thousands of light products to choose from including modern, indoor, and outdoor and bathroom lighting. The range of lights manufacturers, wholesalers we represented is broad. If you are mainly looking for 2019 newest Christmas Tree Light and Christmas Tree Light factory, here you will find all the options you can ever have imagined. \n \n \nFive best LED Christmas Lights to Brighten Your Home & Garden:\nDecorating the Christmas tree with LED lights on this auspicious Christmas festival is quite interesting and fun for the children, adults, and elders. To boost the mood and create a festive environment at home, one must-have LED Christmas Lights that comes at inexpensive rates and offers vibrant colors – red, blue, green, yellow by supporting on glass windows, doors, staircase, and outdoor garden.\n \nThey come in different sizes to add warm, incandescent glow and the plug & play type Christmas lights make easy to install without any hassle. When it comes to choosing the best brand Christmas light, you must always consider the no. of LED’s, string length, material quality, price and warranty information given in “Buying Guide“.\n \nWe’ve done incredible research work on branded Christmas lights by reviewing products online, interacting with customers and brought you the Top 5 Best LED Christmas Lights they’re trending now so go into the products description now,\n \n\nBest LED Christmas Lights for Indoor and Outdoor:\n25 Multicolor Faceted C9 LED Indoor/Outdoor Christmas Light String: The first product on the list is Wintergreen Lightening Christmas String lights. It is one of the best LED Christmas lights that make use of C9 type to fit comfortably at both indoors and outdoors. We’re impressed with the lifespan which is 100000 hours and works efficiently without disturbances. The box contains a set of 25 LED bulbs that emits multiple colors – red, blue, green, yellow, white, etc. For this reason, we’ve given top priority in the list of best brand LED Christmas lights available online. \n \nSpecifications of Wintergreen Christmas String Light:\nUL certified LED light kits.\nEasy to install and setup.\nFeatures are 25 multicolor options.\nPack of 25 C9 LED Christmas lights.\n100000 hours of average lifespan.\nBacked with 3 years of warranty services.\nFull-wave technology for easy accessing.\n\n\n\nThe bulbs use epoxy resist breaking, and cracking materials and emit bright lights as you desire. In a systematic pattern, you can install effortlessly at home interiors, outdoor gardens, and walkways. Full-wave rectifier technology eliminates flicker, pulsing and stroking for a beautiful light display. \nTo make the lights glow vigorously, the female plug is joined with a male plug via end to end connection which is designed to stack. You’ll get 2 extra replacement fuses for the convenience of users.\n \n \n TaoTronics TT-SL036 33ft 100 LED String Lights: Make your home beautiful with the TaoTronics LED Christmas Lights. Although it offers exceptional performance, comes at low-prices to match the user’s requirement. Hence, we’ve given the best budget LED Christmas light on the list.\n \nSpecifications of TaoTronics Christmas lights:\n33 feet of LED wire length.\nAdapter with 5 feet cable.\nMade of eco-friendly materials.\nWeatherproof LED string light.\n100 LED lights for decoration.\nIt offers a 1-year manufacturing warranty.\nIt comes with a remote controller with short circuit protection.\n \nThis amazing device includes a remote controller with 24 buttons to monitor the LED’s lights and set time accordingly. It has power on/off buttons to start/stop and adjust the brightness if required.\nFurther, it is made of eco-friendly copper wire to keep LED’s safe and at low temperature after continuous usage for hours. It can easily be mounded into any shape around furniture, plants, windows, staircase, frames, etc.\nWhen you buy this Christmas light kit online, you’ll get UL certified power adapter, with 5 feet cable to support 33 feet lighting wire + 100 LED’s, remote controller, receiver and a gift box. Given below image show the components provided in the kit.\n \n \nMZD8391 Upgraded 66 FT 200 LED Christmas Lights Outdoor String Lights: Give it a try with MZD8391 Christmas tree lights to decor your home. It brings the immense look to home indoors and joy in children while assembling LED lights on the staircase, doors, and windows.\n \nWhat is in the package? \nGreen string light\nSpare LED beads\nSpare fuse and\nUser-friendly manual\nThe 200 LED Christmas lights are perfect to craft on garden trees, wedding parties and take family pictures, selfies and make it into a frame as memory. This amazing device is highly IP44 waterproof nature and can be used for both indoors/outdoors. You don’t have to worry about the light kit when there is a little or heavy rain outside.  \nSpecifications of MZD8391 Christmas Lights:\nEmits warm white color light.\n12 months manufacturing warranty.\nUses 200 commercial-grade LED bulbs.\nMade of sturdy and durable materials.\n60 days of money-back guarantee scheme.\nSuitable for Christmas Eve, wedding parties.\n \nUnlike other brands, it is made of sturdy, durable copper material and re-usable bulbs for long-term usage. Its build design is such that it can overcome the problems like overheating issues, moisture or weather damage, and short circuit. When the bulb has burned out, you can pull out the burnt LED and insert any of the 4 spare bulbs given by the product manufacturer.\n \nDecute Upgraded 105 Feet 300 LED Christmas String Lights: This is the perfect Christmas lights to have at home because of the IP55 waterproof nature that adds stunning visuals to the home indoors and outdoors. Once, the Christmas season is completed, you can also use for weddings, parties, night events, and so on.\nThe string lights come with 8 lighting modes to choose like flashing, blinking, chasing, fading, etc. and minimize the efforts to select the color every time you switch on the LED lights. It’s simply a plug and play type device that has an end-to-end connection and can be attached to a maximum of 4 strips together i.e. 105 feet of each wire length forming up to 420 feet. You just need to supply a maximum of 120 V using the UL-certified power adapter. The device utilizes less power and is safe to handle because of the shockproof and waterproof nature. That’s why this stylish product is considered as the best waterproof LED Christmas tree lights among the available brands.\n \nSpecifications of Decute Christmas String Lights:\nThe string length is 105 feet.\nIt comes with 8 setting modes.\n100% UL certified LED string light.\n300 LED’s for to decor the home interiors.\nIP55 waterproof design to support both indoors and outdoors.\nTo conclude, this Decute Christmas tree LED’s emits warm white color light and makes the surrounding environment romantic and cheerful. Moreover, it is very easy to install, clean and maintain as well.   \n \nMAXINDA Outdoor LED String Lights: If you’re tired of using cheap-quality LED string lights that don’t even last for 2 days? Now, it’s the right time to shift to MAXINDA outdoor LED string lights. This wonderful device solves all your needs as it comes with 50 LED’s and 18 feet string length. You can easily fix them on walls, glass windows, doors, etc. with less effort.\nThis C3 LED Christmas light comes at low-prices and offers reliable performance throughout the bulb life. As the device is made of environmentally friendly materials, it lasts longer by supporting different climatic conditions outside.\n \nSpecifications of MAXINDA LED String Lights \n3000 hours of LED lifespan.\n50 LED’s bloom in warm white color.\nIt has 18 feet string length to support bulbs.\nDurable and energy-efficient LED lights.\nMade using eco-friendly plastic material.\nBest fits on walls, lawn, yards, parties, etc.\nDustproof, waterproof and fire-resistant nature.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'Greatest festival of led Christmas tree lights', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', '__trashed', '', '', '2019-08-17 10:44:41', '2019-08-17 10:44:41', '', 0, 'http://sajedaiub.com/Development/affiliate_app/?p=186', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(188, 2, '2019-08-16 08:58:41', '2019-08-16 08:58:41', 'White led Christmas lights:\r\nWarm white led light has been a favorite light color with both businesses and residences since 2005. The most fashionable led Christmas light colors are warm or cool white and the decision for many people simply comes down to favorite and color systems.\r\n\r\nCozy and inviting: Warm white led lights clarify indoor spaces with a soft glow that is most often connected with customary mini lights. These cozy hued bulbs look great indoors and outdoors and can be used just about anywhere. Warm white led bulbs are an excellent color balance to Christmas decorating that uses gold ornaments, ribbons, and accents.\r\n\r\nVivid and bright: Cool white led lights are often chosen when people want to achieve a more snow-white tone or if they are creating color patterns. For example, cool white LEDs are well-liked with red, white or blue and white holiday themes. The cool white led lights also very popular as a balance to silver intonation colors with Christmas tree bulbs or ribbon.\r\n\r\nWarm white led Christmas lights:\r\nWarm white led Christmas lights available on in several different styles to form the warm white led c9 and c7 led bulbs, to very popular led c6 strawberry, t5 traditional and the wide-angle led mini lights strings. We also suggest warm white-colored icicle lights and net lights. These energy-efficient and vesicle light sets are for indoor and outdoor use and will provide years of maintenance-free use.\r\n\r\nDecorating with warm white led Christmas lights:\r\nWhether you\'ve always decorated for the holidays, or you\'re just beginning to think about sprucing up your Christmas decor, there are some excellent ideas here for using warm white color led Christmas lights to help you get those creative juices elegant.\r\n\r\nBe concern, warm white color led lights blends with most colors, so you don\'t have to worry about it clashing with your wall paint color or furniture colors. Christmas and holidays aren\'t the only time you can use lights to decorate your home. The customary white wedding is the perfect occasion to use warm white color led Christmas lights to show up.\r\n\r\nWhy use led Christmas lights?\r\nOne major advantage of using led Christmas string lights is their life span and low power consumption. This means you can keep using your warm white Christmas lights for years to come and use more of them.\r\nFor example, a 17-foot incandescent string light with 50 individual lamps has a maximum connection run of 10 strings, but a similar led string light can have 43 strings connected end to end without overloading the circuit. That\'s 170 feet of lights versus 731 feet. Now that\'s a lot of lights to make your home shine this Christmas.\r\n\r\nThe 6 best indoor Christmas lights of 2019:\r\nIn 2019 if you are looking for energy-efficient led lights, we can give you a perfect guide to help you make an informed purchase, but traditional incandescent lights are still an option as well. Here we reviewed some led Christmas tree lights to identify the best of the best, focusing on features such as color, length, number of bulbs, ease of use, and light pattern options. Such as,\r\n\r\nBest overall from koopower 200 led indoor string light:\r\nThese indoor lights from koopower 200 led strings light have every feature you could ever need. The white lights will give off a warm, cozy glow as they’re wrapped around your Christmas tree or decked through the halls.\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for a plain set of Christmas lights, this product is a highly-rated option that comes at a reasonable price. You get 200 white led lights on a clear wire that stretches an impressive 69 feet. The lights are controlled by a wireless remote, which allows you to dim or brighten the bulbs, as well as switch between their eight modes, including twinkle, sequential, flashing and more.\r\n\r\nAdditionally, these string lights come with a built-in timer, which turns them on for six hours a day, letting you enjoy the lights when you’re home and save energy when you’re not. No need to worry about the bulbs getting hot, either, as led lights stay cool, making them safe to use around fabric or other flammable material.\r\n\r\nBest colored lights from holiday wonderland\'s 300-count color light set:\r\nA more exciting Christmas display, you may want a strand of colored holiday lights. In this case, holiday wonderland\'s 300-count mini multi-color Christmas light set is a reasonably priced option to brighten up your home.\r\n\r\nThis set includes two strands of string lights, each with 150 mini multi-colored bulbs in alternating hues including green, red, blue and purple. Each string of lights is 39 feet long and includes end-to-end connectors so they can be plugged in together. The green wire makes these string lights perfect for decorating trees, and if a light goes out, there are several replacement bulbs included in the set, as well as a replacement fuse.\r\n\r\nIf you want to have a colorful Christmas, these mini holiday lights will surely bring cheer into your home—and they won\'t break the bank either.\r\n\r\nBest overall Christmas light from everglow 2980-22 100 clear white wires light set:\r\nFor usual, no-frills Christmas lights, you’ll want the everglow clear white wire light set. These white string lights come at an unbeatable price and will give you the cozy ambiance that you crave during the holiday season.\r\n\r\nEvery everglow white light set contains 100 clear Christmas lights with 2.5-volt bulbs. The string of lights is 20 feet long, with 18 lighted feet, and features white wire. There are end-to-end connectors on each string so you can connect multiple strands and decorate more of your house. The set also comes with several replacement bulbs in case of any burnout.\r\n\r\nIf you’re looking for a set of standard Christmas lights, you should consider the everglow clear white wire light set. They don’t come with any fancy features, but they’re sure to look lovely draped throughout your home during the winter months.\r\n\r\nOur top pick from novelty lights 100 light led Christmas mini light set:\r\nAfter searching high and low, the novelty lights 100 light led Christmas mini lights are extremely well made and can stand up to many years of Christmas-time use. They have a 22 gauge wire and feature 100 lights, spaced six inches apart, with a total length of 50 feet. If you need more lights, you can link multiple strings together (up to 21 in total), since they have a “male” plug on one end and a “female” plug on the other. The green wire blends into your tree’s foliage for a seamless look.\r\n\r\nNot only can you opt for a classic warm white, multicolor lights and plain red lights are also available, so you can pick something to suit your taste or your decorative scheme. Using only 9.6 watts per string, these Christmas tree lights won’t hike up your power bill. While you can’t replace individual bulbs, each one should last for 40,000 hours (that’s 4.5 years of 24-hour use, which equals a lot of Christmases) and the lights comes with a 3-year guarantee for peace of mind.\r\nCosting $20 to $25 per string (depending on which color you choose), these certainly aren’t the cheapest led Christmas tree lights on the market, but they’re worth the extra cost for their longevity.\r\n\r\nNovelty lights 100 light led Christmas mini light set key features:\r\nSuitable for indoor and outdoor use\r\nMeets ul safety standards\r\nCan join multiple strings together\r\n\r\nBest budget pick from accmor 4 pack 30 LEDs mini bulb battery operated string lights:\r\nLooking for an affordable lighting option? These accmor 4 pack 30 LEDs mini bulb battery operated string lights cost just $10 for 4 strings of lights, which is a bargain by anyone’s calculations! It’s worth noting, however, that these strings are on the smaller side—measuring just 10 feet and with 30 lights, so they’re not ideal for decorating very large trees. However, if you have a few small trees to decorate (or you’d like to decorate one small tree and have some lights left over for other decorative features), they’re a perfect choice.\r\n\r\nThese led Christmas tree lights run from a battery pack (which takes 2 aa batteries), which is great if you want to use them somewhere you don’t have easy access to a power socket. You can choose between either having these lights either steady on or flashing on and off.\r\nThese aren’t the sorts of lights that will last a generation, but they’re perfect if you’re looking for Christmas tree lights on a budget.\r\nAccmor 4 pack 30 LEDs mini bulb battery operated string lights key features:\r\nChoice of 2 lighting modes\r\nWarm white color\r\nBattery operated\r\n\r\nBest multicolor led Christmas tree lights from bulbhead star shower tree dazzler led Christmas lights:\r\nThe bulbhead star shower tree dazzler led Christmas lights are different from any others we’ve seen before. Consisting of strings of light hanging vertically from a ring, you simply place the ring on the top of your tree and let the lights hang down, instead of getting in a tangle wrapping a single long string around your tree.\r\n\r\nWhile they’re our best multicolor pick, you can also choose to set them to other solid colors, with a total of 16 color and pattern combinations available. And, if that’s not enough for you, there’s also a “deluxe” option available with 31 settings.\r\n\r\nThe star shower tree dazzler features a total of 8 strands, each with 8 large, bright led bulbs on it. There are some limitations regarding tree height, however, as it’s recommending for use with a tree of roughly 7.5 feet, and might not look as effective on a tree that’s much taller or shorter.\r\nWith a price tag of roughly $50, these do cost a lot more than most other led Christmas tree lights, but most buyers state that it’s well worth shelling out some extra dough for the speed and simplicity of putting them on your tree.\r\n\r\nChristmas lights Bulbhead star shower tree dazzler led key features:\r\nSaves time and effort when trimming your tree\r\nVarious color and pattern settings\r\nEasy-to-use controller\r\n\r\nImportance of white led Christmas light:\r\nWhite led Christmas lights are extremely durable due to their hard plastic casings and do not lose their color the way that painted incandescent bulbs do. Bright white Christmas lights burn only a fraction of the energy as incandescent lights, making them a good choice for saving money, conserving energy, and also helping the environment.\r\n\r\nWhite Christmas lights work for a longer period and have lower operating temperatures than traditional Christmas lights. Led Christmas lights come in different sizes and colors which means they can be used for more than Christmas decorations.\r\n\r\nPure white led Christmas lights are ideal to decorate Christmas tree, outdoor holiday decorating, dining room, walkways, garden path, home, and other buildings. White led Christmas lights to create an attractive and warm feeling and perfect to decorate marriage ceremony parties too.', 'Best warm white led Christmas lights', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'best-warm-white-led-christmas-lights', '', '', '2019-08-16 09:01:50', '2019-08-16 09:01:50', '', 0, 'http://sajedaiub.com/Development/affiliate_app/?p=188', 0, 'post', '', 0),
